    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a project with potential? This car is ready for someone with a vision to bring it back to its former glory! While it's in poor condition and will require some significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic opportunity for a handy owner or someone looking for a budget-friendly restoration project. It's an honest find for the right person ready to roll up their sleeves!",
